  "body": "# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to record and send audios **so that** I can send audio messages in chats. \r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\nThis is a follow up (or part 2) issue on #13515 which implements the record audio button with its animations and touch interactions, without any recording logic. The idea of this issue is to implement the complete audio recording / sending / reviewing / cancelling flow. The audio message is excluded from this issue.\r\n\r\n### Acceptance Criteria\r\n\r\nUser should be able to:\r\n- Record audio by holding & releasing the record button\r\n- Record audio by holding, locking and stopping the audio button  (slide up-left the button while recording)\r\n- Send audio without reviewing the recorded audio (slide up the button while recording)\r\n- Send audio after reviewing the recorded audio\r\n- Cancel recording without reviewing the recorded audio (slide left the button while recording)\r\n- Cancel recording after reviewing the recorded audio\r\n- Reviewing and listening to recorded audio before sending / cancelling audio\r\n\r\nMaximum audio length should be of 2 minutes.\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\n#### Relevant Figma components:\r\n\r\n**Record audio component:** \r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System?node-id=5626%3A158332&t=TbnUk9yl230U7CTN-4\r\n**Soundtrack component:** https://www.figma.com/file/WQZcp6S0EnzxdTL4taoKDv/Design-System?node-id=5626%3A158325&t=TbnUk9yl230U7CTN-4\r\n\r\n#### Visual reference (use Figma as the source of truth)\r\n\r\n<img width=\"362\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/18485527/207924198-e0c6570c-33e0-47a3-b1e1-746c2dbd7fab.png\">",
